				<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
					<font fontName="Times New Roman" size="10"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[If the Tenant pays the first installment of rent by cheque but the cheque is dishonored, the Tenant is in fundamental breach of this Agreement, and this Agreement will be terminated with immediate effect. The Landlord shall have the right to claim compensation from the Tenant for the tenant’s breach of this Agreement. The rental deposit paid by the Tenant upon signing this Agreement will also be forfeited by the Landlord. In this case, the Landlord shall have no obligation to deliver the said shop to the Tenant and shall be released from other obligations under this Agreement. The Tenant shall have no right to claim compensation in any form from the Landlord under this Agreement.]]></text>
			</staticText>
