			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="98" y="455" width="432" height="25" uuid="c379953a-ef92-41ca-bd34-7a45c2054195">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.y" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[倘承租人已根據本租約第IV條(16)款所載規定，向業主交付任何保證書，如業主提出要求，承租人
須自費取得並向承讓人交付一份類似第IV條(16)款所載新簽訂之保證書，惟受惠人須為承讓人。]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="65" y="497" width="464" height="71" uuid="7af2c1dc-b498-48a0-9039-5e48d818f0b9">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="pixel"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.y" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[由上述轉讓復歸權及業主一切權利和業主所須承擔義務之日期起，業主將完全卸除本租約所載有關業主之
一切義務和責任(包括業主按照本租約所載之合約或非合約條款及條件，退還由承租人根據第IV條(15)款
所載之規定而繳付之按金(如有的話)之義務)，而一切該等義務和責任將由承讓人承擔。倘承租人已根據第
IV條(15)款所載之規定繳付任何按金，則承租人只可要求承讓人退還上述按金(有關要求須受本合約之條款
及條件所約束)。]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="43" y="24" width="17" height="15" uuid="037e4f7f-3271-4a14-a2b8-3543b4ba7318"/>
				<textElement>
					<font fontName="Times New Roman" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="1_1_2"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[(15)]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<textField>
				<reportElement x="65" y="24" width="464" height="13" uuid="b1cad678-9fb7-43e7-9644-22e900ab8d84">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="pixel"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["本租約終止時，倘承租人已清繳全部租金及其他應繳之費用、而又並無違約行為者，業主須將承租人在<br>a"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<textField>
				<reportElement x="65" y="37" width="141" height="13" uuid="f8c3a331-f5e1-4631-8beb-65d690a573fc">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["簽訂本合約時所繳交之按金港幣<br>a"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<textField textAdjust="ScaleFont" isBlankWhenNull="true">
				<reportElement x="206" y="37" width="323" height="13" uuid="55205a1a-26f0-4c85-b4a5-50efa18dd0b8">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<box>
					<bottomPen lineWidth="1.0" lineStyle="Solid"/>
				</box>
				<textElement textAlignment="Center" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[ChineseConvertUtil.decimalToChinese($F{DEPOSIT_AMT})]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<textField>
				<reportElement x="65" y="50" width="24" height="13" uuid="cd47dd9e-d4bc-4cf6-9732-e28055638c9b">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="pixel"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["(HK$"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<textField textAdjust="ScaleFont" isBlankWhenNull="true">
				<reportElement x="89" y="50" width="74" height="13" uuid="1a221525-35e7-4821-b84b-354533e8f21d">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<box>
					<bottomPen lineWidth="1.0" lineStyle="Solid"/>
				</box>
				<textElement textAlignment="Center" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[$F{DEPOSIT_AMT}==null || $F{DEPOSIT_AMT}.compareTo(BigDecimal.ZERO) == 0 ? "" :  $F{DEPOSIT_TEXT}]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<textField>
				<reportElement x="163" y="50" width="366" height="13" uuid="58624ef3-833f-4b67-b8aa-7c9cd719f83a">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[")，免息交回承租人。倘有欠租及未清繳其他費用等情，業主可先將按金之全部或一<br>a"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<textField>
				<reportElement x="65" y="63" width="464" height="32" uuid="462e9f69-fd82-43d6-97b0-0ecfe030c033">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="pixel"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["部分扣除撥付。倘承租人有違約行為，業主得在可能範圍內將按金之全部或一部分扣除以補償其損失，<br>並可用其他方式向承租人索償。在此情形下，袛須將按金之餘款(若尚有餘款者)發還承租人。"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="28" y="106" width="15" height="15" uuid="2692aea3-384b-4c2e-a8a1-5d32308a9235">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Right">
					<font fontName="Times New Roman" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="1_1_2"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[*]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="43" y="106" width="17" height="15" uuid="f5961fe7-ccbe-4862-866a-ba8055655ae7"/>
				<textElement>
					<font fontName="Times New Roman" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="1_1_2"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[(16)]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<textField>
				<reportElement x="65" y="106" width="464" height="90" uuid="26e9e565-a577-4271-8942-84abbf4f1726">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="pixel"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["承租人須根據業主所同意之條件，自費向業主所認可之銀行，接受存款公司或保險公司獲取相等於港<br>幣<u>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;</u>(HK$<u>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;</u>)之保證書，以確保如期向業主繳付本租約所列之租<br>金以及妥為遵守及履行本租約之條款(是項責任由承租人及上述銀行或公司共同承擔)，隨後並須將保證<br>書交予業主保管，倘上述租期屆滿時，承租人並無欠繳上述租金任何部份，亦無違反或不履行本租約所<br>載之條款及條件；又或是承租人已根據本租約第IV條(20)款之規定，把新簽訂之保證書交付承讓人以取<br>代上述保證書，則上述保證書得交還承租人。"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="43" y="203" width="17" height="15" uuid="f13843a8-e542-48a8-a250-12826617c510"/>
				<textElement>
					<font fontName="Times New Roman" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="1_1_2"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[(17)]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="65" y="203" width="464" height="25" uuid="e9d65ece-a2b2-4bb7-9dab-98031d3ffee5">
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.width" value="pixel"/>
					<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
				</reportElement>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
					<font fontName="新細明體" size="10"/>
					<paragraph lineSpacing="Single" lineSpacingSize="1.0"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[本租約並不賦予承租人在該邨內經營某種行業之專利權。業主仍有權按照自行鑑定之屋邨需求情況，將
該邨內其他商業單位以任何方式租予他人，以便經營同一行業。]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="28" y="246" width="15" height="15" uuid="4a11a94e-016d-4afd-a9a6-918c3912dc80">
